title: Inslee: Trump Needs to 'Recognize' Constitution Gives Governors the Authority to Reopen
description: Monday on MSNBC, Gov. Jay Inslee (D-WA) said President Donald Trump needed to "recognize" the Constitution gives governors the authority to make the decision to reopen states. | Clips
content:
